To use
1. npm i express-generator -g                                          // installs express generator golobally

2. cd to folder

3. express MySiteName     or   express MySiteName --view=ejs           // creates all the site stuff automagically

4.go to MysiteName folder 

5. npm install                                                          // this will install all the modules automatically


to change the view engin to ejs type : express MySiteName --view=ejs

dont forget to add helmut

you can just type nodemon  and it should just run
